quran[21]{c,v,t}:
  26,40,"LaAAallana nattabiAAu assaharatain kanoo humu alghalibeen"
  26,41,"Falamma jaa assaharatuqaloo lifirAAawna a-inna lana laajran in kunnanahnu alghalibeen"
  26,42,"Qala naAAam wa-innakum ithanlamina almuqarrabeen"
  26,43,"Qala lahum moosa alqoo maantum mulqoon"
  26,44,"Faalqaw hibalahum waAAisiyyahumwaqaloo biAAizzati firAAawna inna lanahnualghaliboon"
  26,45,"Faalqa moosa AAasahufa-itha hiya talqafu ma ya/fikoon"
  26,46,"Faolqiya assaharatu sajideen"
  26,47,"Qaloo amanna birabbialAAalameen"
  26,48,"Rabbi moosa waharoon"
  26,49,"Qala amantum lahu qabla an athanalakum innahu lakabeerukumu allathee AAallamakumu assihrafalasawfa taAAlamoona laoqattiAAanna aydiyakum waarjulakummin khilafin walaosallibannakum ajmaAAeen"
  26,50,"Qaloo la dayra innaila rabbina munqaliboon"
  26,51,"Inna natmaAAu an yaghfira lanarabbuna khatayana an kunnaawwala almu/mineen"
  26,52,"Waawhayna ila moosaan asri biAAibadee innakum muttabaAAoon"
  26,53,"Faarsala firAAawnu fee almada-ini hashireen"
  26,54,"Inna haola-i lashirthimatunqaleeloon"
  26,55,"Wa-innahum lana lagha-ithoon"
  26,56,"Wa-inna lajameeAAun hathiroon"
  26,57,"Faakhrajnahum min jannatinwaAAuyoon"
  26,58,"Wakunoozin wamaqamin kareem"
  26,59,"Kathalika waawrathnahabanee isra-eel"
  26,60,"FaatbaAAoohum mushriqeen"
